1
00:00:04,254 --> 00:00:07,132
<font color="japanese">（小柳(こやなぎ)沙耶香(さやか)）この山で
100枚のコインを集めるのは</c.japanese>

2
00:00:07,257 --> 00:00:08,758
<font color="japanese">至難の業だ</c.japanese>

3
00:00:09,259 --> 00:00:11,094
<font color="japanese">（小柳）だが われわれは</c.japanese>

4
00:00:11,219 --> 00:00:14,723
<font color="japanese">墜落した宇宙船を
捜すというひらめきを得て</c.japanese>

5
00:00:14,931 --> 00:00:16,766
<font color="japanese">すでに場所も割り出した</c.japanese>

6
00:00:17,809 --> 00:00:19,436
<font color="japanese">われわれは弱い</c.japanese>

7
00:00:19,769 --> 00:00:23,273
<font color="japanese">だが 知恵と
切っても切れない結束がある</c.japanese>

8
00:00:23,982 --> 00:00:26,609
<font color="japanese">このゲームは 人間の愚かさを
あぶり出しにする</c.japanese>

9
00:00:27,819 --> 00:00:30,447
<font color="japanese">裏切り合い 殺し合い</c.japanese>

10
00:00:30,947 --> 00:00:34,117
<font color="japanese">山に入った連中は
この醜い欲望を―</c.japanese>

11
00:00:34,242 --> 00:00:37,203
<font color="japanese">バケモノになってまで
貫き通そうとする</c.japanese>

12
00:00:38,121 --> 00:00:40,415
<font color="japanese">だが われわれは愚かではない</c.japanese>

13
00:00:41,041 --> 00:00:43,918
<font color="japanese">バケモノ同然に
卑しく生きるつもりもない</c.japanese>

14
00:00:44,377 --> 00:00:48,173
<font color="japanese">忘れるな たとえ
どんな力を得たとしても</c.japanese>

15
00:00:48,381 --> 00:00:50,508
<font color="japanese">われわれは
あくまで人間として</c.japanese>

16
00:00:51,342 --> 00:00:53,470
<font color="japanese">この 無意味なゲームを
終わらせる</c.japanese>

17
00:00:57,474 --> 00:01:02,479
<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

18
00:02:20,557 --> 00:02:25,562
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

19
00:02:32,610 --> 00:02:35,947
<font color="japanese">（小柳）最近 このあたりで
誰かが戦ったようだな</c.japanese>

20
00:02:36,197 --> 00:02:37,949
<font color="japanese">それも かなり派手に</c.japanese>

21
00:02:38,992 --> 00:02:40,910
<font color="japanese">（加賀谷(かがや)修一(しゅういち)）ここは… あっ</c.japanese>

22
00:02:46,207 --> 00:02:48,042
<font color="japanese">（レンズが動く音）</c.japanese>

23
00:02:49,586 --> 00:02:50,837
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）あっ…！</c.japanese>

24
00:02:51,921 --> 00:02:56,467
<font color="japanese">こいつら やっぱり
何か隠してやがる…</c.japanese>

25
00:03:00,471 --> 00:03:01,598
<font color="japanese">ん？</c.japanese>

26
00:03:03,641 --> 00:03:05,393
<font color="japanese">縄張りのマーク…</c.japanese>

27
00:03:06,227 --> 00:03:08,605
<font color="japanese">（青木(あおき)紅愛(クレア)）この先に
ほかのチームがいるのね</c.japanese>

28
00:03:08,730 --> 00:03:09,731
<font color="japanese">（小柳）そうだ</c.japanese>

29
00:03:10,607 --> 00:03:14,068
<font color="japanese">（クレア）確か あいつも
そんなことを言ってたわね</c.japanese>

30
00:03:14,444 --> 00:03:19,073
<font color="japanese">サンベと戦った時 いつの間にか
縄張りに入っていた</c.japanese>

31
00:03:19,866 --> 00:03:21,743
<font color="japanese">だから あいつが現れた</c.japanese>

32
00:03:22,994 --> 00:03:25,330
<font color="japanese">おそらく
マークの意味は警告だろう</c.japanese>

33
00:03:26,205 --> 00:03:29,584
<font color="japanese">“この先へ進めば攻撃する”
という…</c.japanese>

34
00:03:32,921 --> 00:03:36,466
<font color="japanese">だが 墜落した宇宙船は
ここを抜けた先にある</c.japanese>

35
00:03:36,758 --> 00:03:38,343
<font color="japanese">そこまで たどり着ければ</c.japanese>

36
00:03:39,469 --> 00:03:42,180
<font color="japanese">こいつらより
圧倒的優位に立てる</c.japanese>

37
00:03:42,472 --> 00:03:46,976
<font color="japanese">つまり このまま進んだほうが
相手にとって都合が悪い</c.japanese>

38
00:03:47,352 --> 00:03:51,189
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）正気か？
相手は自分の力に自信があるから</c.japanese>

39
00:03:51,314 --> 00:03:53,483
<font color="japanese">こんな目立つ印を
つけてるんだぞ？</c.japanese>

40
00:03:53,608 --> 00:03:54,984
<font color="japanese">そんなやつらに なんで</c.japanese>

41
00:03:55,401 --> 00:03:57,445
<font color="japanese">何 ピリピリしてるのよ</c.japanese>

42
00:03:57,570 --> 00:04:00,740
<font color="japanese">アンタ 何か
後ろめたいことでもあるの？</c.japanese>

43
00:04:01,157 --> 00:04:02,242
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）なっ！</c.japanese>

44
00:04:02,367 --> 00:04:04,994
<font color="japanese">クレア よしなよ
（クレア）何よ</c.japanese>

45
00:04:05,662 --> 00:04:07,372
<font color="japanese">それくらいにしておけ</c.japanese>

46
00:04:07,705 --> 00:04:09,958
<font color="japanese">池内(いけうち) あれを見せてやれ</c.japanese>

47
00:04:12,293 --> 00:04:13,586
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）分かった</c.japanese>

48
00:04:18,633 --> 00:04:21,636
<font color="japanese">池内が 危険を冒して
偵察してくれたものだ</c.japanese>

49
00:04:22,595 --> 00:04:26,391
<font color="japanese">連中の縄張りは ここから
西のほうに広がっている</c.japanese>

50
00:04:26,724 --> 00:04:31,229
<font color="japanese">ふうん… アンタ
１人で この奥に入ったんだ</c.japanese>

51
00:04:31,354 --> 00:04:33,147
<font color="japanese">よく 無事に帰ってこられたわね
（イケウチ）うっ！</c.japanese>

52
00:04:33,648 --> 00:04:35,525
<font color="japanese">（池内）と… 当然だろ</c.japanese>

53
00:04:36,401 --> 00:04:38,403
<font color="japanese">人数は けっこう多そうね</c.japanese>

54
00:04:38,987 --> 00:04:42,991
<font color="japanese">（村上(むらかみ)陽太(ようた)）
あー なるほど　こいつらか…</c.japanese>

55
00:04:43,116 --> 00:04:46,202
<font color="japanese">クレアちゃんのお姉さんの
江麗奈(エレナ)ちゃんだっけ？</c.japanese>

56
00:04:46,369 --> 00:04:47,954
<font color="japanese">そことやり合ったのは</c.japanese>

57
00:04:48,288 --> 00:04:49,914
<font color="japanese">で どうするんだ？</c.japanese>

58
00:04:50,623 --> 00:04:53,251
<font color="japanese">われわれの目的は
あくまでコインだ</c.japanese>

59
00:04:53,668 --> 00:04:55,169
<font color="japanese">むだな争いは避けたい</c.japanese>

60
00:04:55,962 --> 00:04:58,047
<font color="japanese">多少 遠回りにはなるが</c.japanese>

61
00:04:58,172 --> 00:05:01,092
<font color="japanese">この山を う回して
目的地を目指す</c.japanese>

62
00:05:01,718 --> 00:05:04,137
<font color="japanese">そうね なんにせよ</c.japanese>

63
00:05:04,262 --> 00:05:07,890
<font color="japanese">こんなマークを使うのは
ろくな趣味の連中じゃないわ</c.japanese>

64
00:05:08,516 --> 00:05:11,269
<font color="japanese">池内 周囲の監視を頼む</c.japanese>

65
00:05:11,477 --> 00:05:12,478
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）え？</c.japanese>

66
00:05:12,645 --> 00:05:15,148
<font color="japanese">この先は お前の力が頼りだ</c.japanese>

67
00:05:16,024 --> 00:05:18,192
<font color="japanese">（池内）分かった 任せてくれ</c.japanese>

68
00:05:18,651 --> 00:05:22,363
<font color="japanese">ありがとう 僕も
匂いには気をつけておくから</c.japanese>

69
00:05:22,488 --> 00:05:25,033
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）
フン！　まあ 勝手にしろ</c.japanese>

70
00:05:32,999 --> 00:05:35,835
<font color="japanese">（吉岡(よしおか)千尋(ちひろ)の荒い息遣い）</c.japanese>

71
00:05:35,960 --> 00:05:38,296
<font color="japanese">（修一）大丈夫？
（吉岡）ありがとう</c.japanese>

72
00:05:39,047 --> 00:05:42,467
<font color="japanese">まだ 先は長いし
無理はしないでいいから</c.japanese>

73
00:05:42,592 --> 00:05:43,801
<font color="japanese">（吉岡）うん</c.japanese>

74
00:05:49,599 --> 00:05:52,060
<font color="japanese">（小柳）ハァ… うあっ！</c.japanese>

75
00:05:53,436 --> 00:05:54,937
<font color="japanese">（小柳）あっ…</c.japanese>

76
00:05:55,271 --> 00:05:56,647
<font color="japanese">（相原(あいはら)未来(みく)）クッ…
（小柳）うっ…</c.japanese>

77
00:05:57,398 --> 00:06:00,318
<font color="japanese">（相原）大丈夫ですか？
（小柳）すまない</c.japanese>

78
00:06:01,319 --> 00:06:02,445
<font color="japanese">（相原）いえ…</c.japanese>

79
00:06:08,076 --> 00:06:09,911
<font color="japanese">（小柳）少し休憩しよう</c.japanese>

80
00:06:19,337 --> 00:06:21,339
<font color="japanese">（草が生える音）</c.japanese>

81
00:06:22,423 --> 00:06:23,424
<font color="japanese">（修一）あ…</c.japanese>

82
00:06:27,095 --> 00:06:31,140
<font color="japanese">すごい 勇(いさお)君
こんなこともできるんだ</c.japanese>

83
00:06:31,265 --> 00:06:32,642
<font color="japanese">（カスガのてれ笑い）</c.japanese>

84
00:06:35,186 --> 00:06:36,354
<font color="japanese">はむっ</c.japanese>

85
00:06:36,479 --> 00:06:38,022
<font color="japanese">（飲み込む音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（修一）おいしい！</c.japanese>

86
00:06:38,523 --> 00:06:40,483
<font color="japanese">冷えてれば
もっとよかったのに</c.japanese>

87
00:06:41,109 --> 00:06:43,820
<font color="japanese">もう３つめ？
食べるの早いよ</c.japanese>

88
00:06:43,945 --> 00:06:47,156
<font color="japanese">修一が遅いのよ
（修一）ああ…</c.japanese>

89
00:06:47,323 --> 00:06:49,033
<font color="japanese">（レンズが動く音）</c.japanese>

90
00:06:49,408 --> 00:06:51,786
<font color="japanese">胸の谷間とか撮るなよ
（イケウチ）うっ！</c.japanese>

91
00:06:52,161 --> 00:06:55,456
<font color="japanese">なんのかんの言っても
悪い子じゃないぜ</c.japanese>

92
00:06:55,748 --> 00:06:57,291
<font color="japanese">お前が連れてきた子だしな</c.japanese>

93
00:06:57,667 --> 00:06:58,876
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）うう…</c.japanese>

94
00:06:59,252 --> 00:07:02,255
<font color="japanese">（春日(かすが) 勇）お疲れさまです
池内君も どうぞ</c.japanese>

95
00:07:02,380 --> 00:07:04,048
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）
俺は仕事があるから</c.japanese>

96
00:07:04,173 --> 00:07:06,551
<font color="japanese">この先も
池内君の力が頼りだし</c.japanese>

97
00:07:07,468 --> 00:07:09,887
<font color="japanese">あんまり気を張ったままだと
もたないよ</c.japanese>

98
00:07:10,471 --> 00:07:12,140
<font color="japanese">勇の言うとおりだぜ</c.japanese>

99
00:07:13,766 --> 00:07:16,519
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）一応 もらっておく…
（春日）ウフッ</c.japanese>

100
00:07:17,103 --> 00:07:20,940
<font color="japanese">のんきなものね
まだ何も始まってもいないのに</c.japanese>

101
00:07:21,065 --> 00:07:23,401
<font color="japanese">クレアだって
スイカ食べてるじゃない</c.japanese>

102
00:07:23,526 --> 00:07:26,446
<font color="japanese">これはエネルギーの補充よ
（修一）ああ…</c.japanese>

103
00:07:28,322 --> 00:07:31,993
<font color="japanese">でも こういうの
大事だと思うよ</c.japanese>

104
00:07:32,618 --> 00:07:34,662
<font color="japanese">チームでやってくならね</c.japanese>

105
00:07:37,165 --> 00:07:38,166
<font color="japanese">（吉岡）やっぱり…</c.japanese>

106
00:07:42,545 --> 00:07:44,755
<font color="japanese">みんなに教えなきゃいけない</c.japanese>

107
00:07:46,007 --> 00:07:50,887
<font color="japanese">もうすでに コイン100枚
集めた人がいるってことを…</c.japanese>

108
00:07:52,180 --> 00:07:54,182
<font color="japanese">あの…
（小柳）そろそろ出発しよう</c.japanese>

109
00:07:56,142 --> 00:07:58,936
<font color="japanese">（吉岡のため息）</c.japanese>

110
00:08:06,194 --> 00:08:08,905
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）大丈夫
この先は安全だ</c.japanese>

111
00:08:16,662 --> 00:08:18,915
<font color="japanese">（匂いを嗅ぐ音）</c.japanese>

112
00:08:19,540 --> 00:08:21,834
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）俺の言うことが
信じられないのか？</c.japanese>

113
00:08:22,710 --> 00:08:24,795
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）
ごめん でも この山では</c.japanese>

114
00:08:24,921 --> 00:08:26,797
<font color="japanese">警戒するに
越したことはないから</c.japanese>

115
00:08:27,006 --> 00:08:28,299
<font color="japanese">（レンズが動く音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）クッ…</c.japanese>

116
00:08:29,342 --> 00:08:32,261
<font color="japanese">このルートは危険よ
引き返しましょう</c.japanese>

117
00:08:32,887 --> 00:08:36,015
<font color="japanese">（小柳）なぜだ？
地図では目的地に向かっている</c.japanese>

118
00:08:36,641 --> 00:08:38,976
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）俺のレンズには
何も映っていないぞ！</c.japanese>

119
00:08:39,519 --> 00:08:43,064
<font color="japanese">さっき 別のチームの
マークがあったわよね</c.japanese>

120
00:08:43,189 --> 00:08:44,357
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）あったよ！</c.japanese>

121
00:08:44,482 --> 00:08:47,276
<font color="japanese">だから そいつらの縄張りを
う回しているんだろ！</c.japanese>

122
00:08:47,902 --> 00:08:50,029
<font color="japanese">問題は その縄張りよ</c.japanese>

123
00:08:50,655 --> 00:08:54,492
<font color="japanese">この山で縄張りを張る理由…
なんだと思う？</c.japanese>

124
00:08:57,078 --> 00:09:00,248
<font color="japanese">ほかの“収集者”に
コインを拾われないためよ</c.japanese>

125
00:09:00,706 --> 00:09:03,000
<font color="japanese">だとしたら 不自然じゃない？</c.japanese>

126
00:09:04,001 --> 00:09:07,380
<font color="japanese">さっきのマークがあった
急斜面の 暗い森と</c.japanese>

127
00:09:07,547 --> 00:09:10,967
<font color="japanese">それほど距離の離れていない
この開けた河原</c.japanese>

128
00:09:11,509 --> 00:09:15,304
<font color="japanese">コインを探すのに
どっちが適してると思う？</c.japanese>

129
00:09:16,639 --> 00:09:18,891
<font color="japanese">ここは コインもそうだけど</c.japanese>

130
00:09:19,016 --> 00:09:21,811
<font color="japanese">私たちの姿も
周囲から丸見えよ</c.japanese>

131
00:09:22,478 --> 00:09:25,439
<font color="japanese">もし あれが
縄張りのマークじゃないとしたら</c.japanese>

132
00:09:25,982 --> 00:09:28,943
<font color="japanese">例えばそう
もし あのマークが―</c.japanese>

133
00:09:29,443 --> 00:09:31,862
<font color="japanese">それを避けた
弱い“収集者”を</c.japanese>

134
00:09:32,488 --> 00:09:34,532
<font color="japanese">ここにおびき寄せるための―</c.japanese>

135
00:09:39,537 --> 00:09:41,539
<font color="japanese">わなだったとしたら…</c.japanese>

136
00:09:42,540 --> 00:09:46,460
<font color="japanese">どうやら 少しは
知恵の回る仲間がいるようね</c.japanese>

137
00:09:47,003 --> 00:09:48,004
<font color="japanese">どうする？</c.japanese>

138
00:09:48,462 --> 00:09:50,339
<font color="japanese">距離はそれなりにあるわね</c.japanese>

139
00:09:50,881 --> 00:09:52,008
<font color="japanese">けど…</c.japanese>

140
00:09:52,133 --> 00:09:54,468
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）数が… 多い…</c.japanese>

141
00:09:55,136 --> 00:09:57,555
<font color="japanese">（小柳）落ち着け 大丈夫だ</c.japanese>

142
00:09:57,930 --> 00:10:02,226
<font color="japanese">確かに われわれは弱いが
逃げるのは得意だ</c.japanese>

143
00:10:03,352 --> 00:10:06,814
<font color="japanese">（炭谷）あ 逃げてく
気付かれたか…</c.japanese>

144
00:10:06,939 --> 00:10:10,526
<font color="japanese">（田口）
６… ７… ８人か</c.japanese>

145
00:10:10,818 --> 00:10:12,778
<font color="japanese">数で言えば 有利だが</c.japanese>

146
00:10:13,029 --> 00:10:16,324
<font color="japanese">こちらにも
多少の犠牲は出そうだな</c.japanese>

147
00:10:16,657 --> 00:10:19,285
<font color="japanese">（円(まどか)）お前ら 本当にバカだな</c.japanese>

148
00:10:19,785 --> 00:10:23,289
<font color="japanese">大事な仲間を減らして
どうすんだよ</c.japanese>

149
00:10:24,081 --> 00:10:26,542
<font color="japanese">１人 捕まえればいいんだよ</c.japanese>

150
00:10:27,043 --> 00:10:30,880
<font color="japanese">１人 捕まえて
そいつをかわいがってやれば</c.japanese>

151
00:10:31,547 --> 00:10:32,548
<font color="japanese">（舌なめずり）</c.japanese>

152
00:10:33,049 --> 00:10:35,384
<font color="japanese">（円）あとのやつらも
芋づる式で</c.japanese>

153
00:10:35,509 --> 00:10:38,763
<font color="japanese">俺のコイン集めに
協力してくれる</c.japanese>

154
00:10:38,888 --> 00:10:42,391
<font color="japanese">（モリタの笑い声）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）だったら俺に任せな！</c.japanese>

155
00:10:43,434 --> 00:10:45,770
<font color="japanese">先走りやがって…</c.japanese>

156
00:10:51,776 --> 00:10:53,027
<font color="japanese">（小柳）こっちだ</c.japanese>

157
00:11:00,826 --> 00:11:02,036
<font color="japanese">（小柳）あっ！</c.japanese>

158
00:11:07,875 --> 00:11:10,753
<font color="japanese">（小柳）まさか こんなに早く…</c.japanese>

159
00:11:11,003 --> 00:11:12,713
<font color="japanese">追いつかれるなんて…</c.japanese>

160
00:11:17,468 --> 00:11:18,636
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）下がって</c.japanese>

161
00:11:21,472 --> 00:11:23,099
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）ヒャッハ～！</c.japanese>

162
00:11:23,224 --> 00:11:26,519
<font color="japanese">ビビったか？　俺のスピードに</c.japanese>

163
00:11:26,894 --> 00:11:29,897
<font color="japanese">ああ バケモノらしい
不気味さだ</c.japanese>

164
00:11:30,189 --> 00:11:32,358
<font color="japanese">黙れよ イケメン</c.japanese>

165
00:11:32,483 --> 00:11:35,778
<font color="japanese">顔がよけりゃ
なんでも許されると思うな</c.japanese>

166
00:11:36,278 --> 00:11:39,782
<font color="japanese">俺がすごいのは
スピードだけじゃないぜ</c.japanese>

167
00:11:41,158 --> 00:11:44,537
<font color="japanese">（クレア）たぶん
こいつの目的は時間稼ぎ</c.japanese>

168
00:11:44,912 --> 00:11:46,789
<font color="japanese">私たちを ここに足止めし―</c.japanese>

169
00:11:47,289 --> 00:11:49,750
<font color="japanese">仲間が来るのを
待つための…</c.japanese>

170
00:11:50,459 --> 00:11:53,087
<font color="japanese">だったら
それにつきあう必要は</c.japanese>

171
00:11:53,212 --> 00:11:54,213
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）ない！</c.japanese>

172
00:11:54,672 --> 00:11:55,673
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）おっと</c.japanese>

173
00:12:00,803 --> 00:12:01,887
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）うっ！</c.japanese>

174
00:12:03,097 --> 00:12:04,306
<font color="japanese">（小柳）あっ！</c.japanese>

175
00:12:04,598 --> 00:12:06,767
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）グッ！　クゥ…</c.japanese>

176
00:12:13,149 --> 00:12:14,150
<font color="japanese">ぐあっ！</c.japanese>

177
00:12:17,445 --> 00:12:18,529
<font color="japanese">（小柳）あっ！</c.japanese>

178
00:12:19,822 --> 00:12:21,490
<font color="japanese">（小柳）あっ！　うっ！
（一同）あっ！</c.japanese>

179
00:12:21,699 --> 00:12:24,702
<font color="japanese">（モリタの笑い声）</c.japanese>

180
00:12:28,080 --> 00:12:29,165
<font color="japanese">はっ… クッ！</c.japanese>

181
00:12:29,290 --> 00:12:30,458
<font color="japanese">動くんじゃねえ！</c.japanese>

182
00:12:30,749 --> 00:12:32,001
<font color="japanese">（相原）はっ…</c.japanese>

183
00:12:34,587 --> 00:12:37,298
<font color="japanese">（クレア）クッ… うっ…</c.japanese>

184
00:12:38,507 --> 00:12:41,177
<font color="japanese">（クレア）
やって… くれるじゃない…</c.japanese>

185
00:12:41,635 --> 00:12:44,472
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）まあ
そんなに突っかかるなよ</c.japanese>

186
00:12:44,763 --> 00:12:48,684
<font color="japanese">何も 俺たちは
世界征服がしたいとか</c.japanese>

187
00:12:48,809 --> 00:12:51,854
<font color="japanese">人類抹殺とか
言ってるんじゃねえんだ</c.japanese>

188
00:12:53,147 --> 00:12:54,565
<font color="japanese">（小柳）クッ！　うっ…</c.japanese>

189
00:12:56,734 --> 00:12:58,527
<font color="japanese">あっ！　クッ…</c.japanese>

190
00:12:58,736 --> 00:13:02,031
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）
コインを集めて何をするか？</c.japanese>

191
00:13:02,490 --> 00:13:05,534
<font color="japanese">ガキにだって分かる
簡単な話だ</c.japanese>

192
00:13:06,076 --> 00:13:10,789
<font color="japanese">誰だって同じだろ？
好き勝手に生きてえだけさ</c.japanese>

193
00:13:10,915 --> 00:13:14,668
<font color="japanese">自分たちさえ
幸せになれれば</c.japanese>

194
00:13:15,336 --> 00:13:17,379
<font color="japanese">それでいいんだよ</c.japanese>

195
00:13:17,922 --> 00:13:19,757
<font color="japanese">（小柳のうめき声）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（村上）クッ！</c.japanese>

196
00:13:20,966 --> 00:13:25,387
<font color="japanese">持ってるコインを渡して
俺たちの仲間に入れよ</c.japanese>

197
00:13:26,347 --> 00:13:28,098
<font color="japanese">断れば…</c.japanese>

198
00:13:28,599 --> 00:13:30,935
<font color="japanese">全員 殺す</c.japanese>

199
00:13:31,477 --> 00:13:32,770
<font color="japanese">（一同のおびえる声）</c.japanese>

200
00:13:33,479 --> 00:13:35,773
<font color="japanese">悪い話じゃねえだろ</c.japanese>

201
00:13:36,106 --> 00:13:38,984
<font color="japanese">みんなで一緒に
楽しくやろうぜ</c.japanese>

202
00:13:39,902 --> 00:13:41,195
<font color="japanese">クッ…</c.japanese>

203
00:13:42,196 --> 00:13:43,572
<font color="japanese">ゲス野郎…</c.japanese>

204
00:13:44,114 --> 00:13:46,408
<font color="japanese">はあ？　なんだって？</c.japanese>

205
00:13:46,534 --> 00:13:49,078
<font color="japanese">きれいぶったこと
言ってんじゃねえぞ</c.japanese>

206
00:13:49,578 --> 00:13:52,957
<font color="japanese">てめえらだって
バケモノに違いねえだろ</c.japanese>

207
00:13:53,249 --> 00:13:58,170
<font color="japanese">そうだ お前たちが
仲間に入りたくなるように</c.japanese>

208
00:13:58,921 --> 00:14:01,382
<font color="japanese">いいものを見せてやる</c.japanese>

209
00:14:02,216 --> 00:14:03,217
<font color="japanese">（吉岡）あっ…</c.japanese>

210
00:14:04,009 --> 00:14:06,220
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）袋から出すなよ</c.japanese>

211
00:14:06,845 --> 00:14:09,682
<font color="japanese">（吉岡）ヒッ！
（モリタ）臭えからな</c.japanese>

212
00:14:10,057 --> 00:14:11,016
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）
そいつは 正真正銘本物だ</c.japanese>

213
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:13,686
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）
そいつは 正真正銘本物だ</c.japanese>

214
00:14:11,016 --> 00:14:13,686
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（吉岡のおびえる声）</c.japanese>

215
00:14:14,270 --> 00:14:16,981
<font color="japanese">前に お前らと同じように</c.japanese>

216
00:14:17,273 --> 00:14:21,193
<font color="japanese">俺たちの縄張りに
迷い込んだ女がいてな</c.japanese>

217
00:14:21,777 --> 00:14:24,321
<font color="japanese">仲間に入るのを断って</c.japanese>

218
00:14:24,446 --> 00:14:27,116
<font color="japanese">うちのボスに殺された</c.japanese>

219
00:14:27,616 --> 00:14:30,995
<font color="japanese">うちのボスは
とんでもなく強いぜ</c.japanese>

220
00:14:31,120 --> 00:14:33,706
<font color="japanese">桁違いのバケモノだ</c.japanese>

221
00:14:35,374 --> 00:14:39,336
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）ヒッヒ…
効果てきめんだな</c.japanese>

222
00:14:40,212 --> 00:14:44,425
<font color="japanese">気持ちわりいの我慢して
持ってきて正解だったぜ</c.japanese>

223
00:14:45,301 --> 00:14:46,802
<font color="japanese">クッ…</c.japanese>

224
00:14:54,018 --> 00:14:56,020
<font color="japanese">かわいそうにな…</c.japanese>

225
00:14:58,314 --> 00:15:00,524
<font color="japanese">けっこう美人じゃねえか</c.japanese>

226
00:15:03,193 --> 00:15:04,737
<font color="japanese">俺のタイプだわ</c.japanese>

227
00:15:07,323 --> 00:15:09,867
<font color="japanese">この子が お前らに
なんかしたのか？</c.japanese>

228
00:15:10,159 --> 00:15:13,370
<font color="japanese">関係ねーよ　言っただろ</c.japanese>

229
00:15:13,871 --> 00:15:17,333
<font color="japanese">自分さえ楽しければ
それでいーんだよ！</c.japanese>

230
00:15:18,751 --> 00:15:19,919
<font color="japanese">うっ！</c.japanese>

231
00:15:20,336 --> 00:15:22,546
<font color="japanese">（村上）正直言うと 俺さ</c.japanese>

232
00:15:23,130 --> 00:15:26,425
<font color="japanese">戦いとか
あまり好きじゃないんだよ</c.japanese>

233
00:15:26,967 --> 00:15:31,096
<font color="japanese">昔 ケンカが原因で
高校 辞めたから</c.japanese>

234
00:15:32,139 --> 00:15:35,392
<font color="japanese">友達を守るため
相手を殴ったんだけど―</c.japanese>

235
00:15:35,684 --> 00:15:37,770
<font color="japanese">大けがさせちゃってさ</c.japanese>

236
00:15:39,438 --> 00:15:42,524
<font color="japanese">人間の力で殴って
それだぜ…</c.japanese>

237
00:15:43,108 --> 00:15:45,736
<font color="japanese">もし 今のバケモノの俺が―</c.japanese>

238
00:15:46,987 --> 00:15:51,283
<font color="japanese">本気で人を殴ったら
どうなるかって考えたらさあ</c.japanese>

239
00:15:52,451 --> 00:15:56,330
<font color="japanese">（修一）違う…
僕は　勘違いをしていた…</c.japanese>

240
00:15:57,373 --> 00:15:59,875
<font color="japanese">この人から
ほかの“収集者”のような</c.japanese>

241
00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:03,921
<font color="japanese">威圧感を感じなかったら
気付かなかっただけだ</c.japanese>

242
00:16:05,005 --> 00:16:06,256
<font color="japanese">本当は…</c.japanese>

243
00:16:07,508 --> 00:16:08,759
<font color="japanese">この人は…</c.japanese>

244
00:16:09,927 --> 00:16:11,178
<font color="japanese">強い！</c.japanese>

245
00:16:12,721 --> 00:16:17,685
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）けど まあ
お前なら本気で殴っていいよな</c.japanese>

246
00:16:18,352 --> 00:16:21,271
<font color="japanese">ちょっと待て！
俺に手を出せば この女を…</c.japanese>

247
00:16:23,649 --> 00:16:24,775
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）このっ…</c.japanese>

248
00:16:26,026 --> 00:16:28,278
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）フンッ！
（モリタ）チイッ！</c.japanese>

249
00:16:29,947 --> 00:16:31,240
<font color="japanese">フッ！</c.japanese>

250
00:16:32,741 --> 00:16:33,784
<font color="japanese">あっ！</c.japanese>

251
00:16:34,994 --> 00:16:36,578
<font color="japanese">（骨が砕ける音）</c.japanese>

252
00:16:36,745 --> 00:16:37,746
<font color="japanese">ぐあっ！</c.japanese>

253
00:16:38,747 --> 00:16:40,624
<font color="japanese">（小柳）うっ…
（相原）リーダー！</c.japanese>

254
00:16:42,167 --> 00:16:44,211
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）あ？　なんだって？</c.japanese>

255
00:16:46,171 --> 00:16:47,214
<font color="japanese">（殴る音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（モリタ）あがっ！</c.japanese>

256
00:16:50,342 --> 00:16:52,761
<font color="japanese">（モリタのうめき声）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）ごめん</c.japanese>

257
00:16:52,886 --> 00:16:55,639
<font color="japanese">さっき なんて言ったか
聞こえなかった</c.japanese>

258
00:16:56,348 --> 00:16:58,225
<font color="japanese">もう１回 言え
（モリタ）ガッ…</c.japanese>

259
00:16:58,517 --> 00:17:00,185
<font color="japanese">言ってみろ クソゴミ！</c.japanese>

260
00:17:00,769 --> 00:17:02,688
<font color="japanese">（蹴る音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）あ？　あ？</c.japanese>

261
00:17:02,980 --> 00:17:05,107
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）クッ！
（小柳）もういい 陽太</c.japanese>

262
00:17:05,774 --> 00:17:08,527
<font color="japanese">わりい…
つい カッとなって</c.japanese>

263
00:17:09,111 --> 00:17:12,281
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）まさか…
殺してないだろうな…</c.japanese>

264
00:17:12,448 --> 00:17:14,742
<font color="japanese">（モリタのうめき声）</c.japanese>

265
00:17:16,160 --> 00:17:19,580
<font color="japanese">まあ 生きてはいるっぽいわね</c.japanese>

266
00:17:20,039 --> 00:17:22,541
<font color="japanese">だが 正直 驚いた</c.japanese>

267
00:17:23,000 --> 00:17:27,087
<font color="japanese">この山に入った時から
こういう事態は想定していたが</c.japanese>

268
00:17:27,671 --> 00:17:32,009
<font color="japanese">まさか 人間の死体を
脅しに使うようなクズまでいるとは</c.japanese>

269
00:17:32,634 --> 00:17:36,221
<font color="japanese">目的のためなら 何をしても
いいとでも思っているのか？</c.japanese>

270
00:17:36,930 --> 00:17:38,223
<font color="japanese">ヘドが出る</c.japanese>

271
00:17:38,724 --> 00:17:40,893
<font color="japanese">（イケウチ）そんなこと
言ってる場合か！</c.japanese>

272
00:17:41,018 --> 00:17:43,228
<font color="japanese">どうすんだよ
こんなやつら 敵に回して！</c.japanese>

273
00:17:44,104 --> 00:17:45,773
<font color="japanese">（クレア）いーじゃない 別に</c.japanese>

274
00:17:46,356 --> 00:17:49,985
<font color="japanese">どのみち 目的の宇宙船は
この先にあるんだし</c.japanese>

275
00:17:50,194 --> 00:17:51,945
<font color="japanese">このまま 進めばいいのよ</c.japanese>

276
00:17:52,696 --> 00:17:55,115
<font color="japanese">（小柳）ああ… そうだな</c.japanese>

277
00:17:55,908 --> 00:17:57,201
<font color="japanese">先を急ぐぞ</c.japanese>

278
00:18:06,126 --> 00:18:07,753
<font color="japanese">（円）見失った</c.japanese>

279
00:18:08,629 --> 00:18:10,672
<font color="japanese">足跡も見当たらねえ</c.japanese>

280
00:18:11,006 --> 00:18:14,802
<font color="japanese">花川(はなかわ) お前の透視で
見えるか？</c.japanese>

281
00:18:17,513 --> 00:18:20,724
<font color="japanese">（花川）ここからまっすぐ
500メートル先</c.japanese>

282
00:18:20,849 --> 00:18:23,602
<font color="japanese">裸までバッチリ見えるぜ</c.japanese>

283
00:18:24,394 --> 00:18:28,023
{\an8}<font color="japanese">（モリタのうめき声）</c.japanese>

284
00:18:24,394 --> 00:18:28,023
<font color="japanese">（虻川(あぶかわ)）ひでえな これ
下顎 なくなってるじゃねえか</c.japanese>

285
00:18:28,023 --> 00:18:28,816
<font color="japanese">（虻川(あぶかわ)）ひでえな これ
下顎 なくなってるじゃねえか</c.japanese>

286
00:18:29,441 --> 00:18:31,610
<font color="japanese">これじゃ 飯も食えねえだろ</c.japanese>

287
00:18:31,735 --> 00:18:34,321
<font color="japanese">（炭谷）もともと
ブサイクなやつだったけど</c.japanese>

288
00:18:34,446 --> 00:18:36,323
<font color="japanese">ここまで来ると 笑えるな</c.japanese>

289
00:18:36,865 --> 00:18:38,575
<font color="japanese">（田口）どうする？　円</c.japanese>

290
00:18:38,784 --> 00:18:40,786
<font color="japanese">まあ しかたねえよな</c.japanese>

291
00:18:40,911 --> 00:18:44,081
<font color="japanese">調子に乗って １人で
勝手に飛び出したんだ</c.japanese>

292
00:18:44,206 --> 00:18:47,000
<font color="japanese">（モリタのうめき声）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（円）そいつはもう 役に立たねえ</c.japanese>

293
00:18:47,584 --> 00:18:50,003
<font color="japanese">（岡本）役に立たねえなら
殺しちゃえば？</c.japanese>

294
00:18:50,129 --> 00:18:52,422
<font color="japanese">前から嫌いだったんだよ
そいつ</c.japanese>

295
00:18:52,548 --> 00:18:55,384
<font color="japanese">（金城）俺もだ
やること 悪趣味だし</c.japanese>

296
00:18:55,509 --> 00:18:57,636
<font color="japanese">やたら人をバカにするし</c.japanese>

297
00:18:58,095 --> 00:19:00,639
<font color="japanese">（円）
お前ら ホントにクソだな</c.japanese>

298
00:19:01,265 --> 00:19:05,310
<font color="japanese">ミスぐらいするだろ
お前ら バカなんだから</c.japanese>

299
00:19:06,186 --> 00:19:10,274
<font color="japanese">分かってると思うが
お前らのボスも</c.japanese>

300
00:19:10,399 --> 00:19:13,235
<font color="japanese">コインを集め
力を手に入れるのも</c.japanese>

301
00:19:13,360 --> 00:19:14,653
<font color="japanese">この俺だ</c.japanese>

302
00:19:15,195 --> 00:19:18,240
<font color="japanese">だから 俺は
証明しなきゃならねえ</c.japanese>

303
00:19:19,116 --> 00:19:22,870
<font color="japanese">俺がお前らのボスに
ふさわしいってことを</c.japanese>

304
00:19:23,245 --> 00:19:25,622
<font color="japanese">分かるか？　森田(もりた)</c.japanese>

305
00:19:27,207 --> 00:19:28,876
<font color="japanese">（円のうなり声）</c.japanese>

306
00:19:29,751 --> 00:19:31,587
<font color="japanese">（円）お前らの痛みは</c.japanese>

307
00:19:32,254 --> 00:19:33,463
<font color="japanese">（歯が抜ける音）</c.japanese>

308
00:19:34,882 --> 00:19:36,341
<font color="japanese">俺の痛みだ</c.japanese>

309
00:19:37,301 --> 00:19:40,637
<font color="japanese">俺は 何があっても
お前らを見捨てねえ</c.japanese>

310
00:19:40,929 --> 00:19:44,141
<font color="japanese">（モリタの泣き声）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（円）お前らがどんなに</c.japanese>

311
00:19:44,266 --> 00:19:46,768
<font color="japanese">最低のクソ野郎どもでもな</c.japanese>

312
00:19:47,102 --> 00:19:49,146
<font color="japanese">（一同の雄たけび）</c.japanese>

313
00:19:49,730 --> 00:19:52,024
<font color="japanese">そこで待ってろ 森田</c.japanese>

314
00:19:52,232 --> 00:19:55,777
<font color="japanese">あいつらを
お前と同じ顔にしてやる</c.japanese>

315
00:20:00,032 --> 00:20:02,868
<font color="japanese">（木が生える音）</c.japanese>

316
00:20:05,329 --> 00:20:08,415
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）すごい
まるで バリケードだ</c.japanese>

317
00:20:08,540 --> 00:20:10,375
<font color="japanese">（クレア）大した能力ね</c.japanese>

318
00:20:10,500 --> 00:20:12,961
<font color="japanese">これなら
追いつかれる心配もないわ</c.japanese>

319
00:20:13,462 --> 00:20:14,922
<font color="japanese">（カスガのてれ笑い）</c.japanese>

320
00:20:15,505 --> 00:20:16,965
<font color="japanese">（小柳）先を急ぐぞ</c.japanese>

321
00:20:17,299 --> 00:20:21,303
<font color="japanese">クレア お前はシューイチの中に
入らなくていいのか？</c.japanese>

322
00:20:21,428 --> 00:20:25,182
<font color="japanese">あの中は暑いからね
そう 何十分も入ってられない…</c.japanese>

323
00:20:25,307 --> 00:20:27,643
<font color="japanese">（破壊する音）</c.japanese>
<font color="japanese">（一同）ハッ！</c.japanese>

324
00:20:29,645 --> 00:20:32,064
<font color="japanese">（破壊する音）</c.japanese>

325
00:20:37,819 --> 00:20:39,488
<font color="japanese">（カスガ）ぐあっ！</c.japanese>

326
00:20:58,090 --> 00:20:59,341
<font color="japanese">（マドカ）お前だろ</c.japanese>

327
00:20:59,925 --> 00:21:03,262
<font color="japanese">うちの かわいい森田を
やったのは</c.japanese>

328
00:21:06,056 --> 00:21:07,432
<font color="japanese">俺だよ！</c.japanese>

329
00:21:16,942 --> 00:21:18,235
<font color="japanese">なっ！</c.japanese>

330
00:21:21,238 --> 00:21:23,657
<font color="japanese">（クレア）修一！
（マドカ）んっ？</c.japanese>

331
00:21:23,782 --> 00:21:25,325
<font color="japanese">んっ… クッ…</c.japanese>

332
00:21:26,159 --> 00:21:27,786
<font color="japanese">（舌なめずり）</c.japanese>

333
00:21:31,498 --> 00:21:33,709
<font color="japanese">（池内）な… なんなんだ…</c.japanese>

334
00:21:34,376 --> 00:21:35,794
<font color="japanese">こいつは…</c.japanese>

335
00:21:37,754 --> 00:21:39,339
<font color="japanese">（池内のおびえる声）</c.japanese>

336
00:21:40,549 --> 00:21:44,261
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）おい
俺を無視してんじゃねえよ</c.japanese>

337
00:21:45,846 --> 00:21:47,139
<font color="japanese">おい…</c.japanese>

338
00:21:47,389 --> 00:21:49,766
<font color="japanese">やめろ… 陽太…</c.japanese>

339
00:21:50,475 --> 00:21:51,727
<font color="japanese">おい！</c.japanese>

340
00:21:52,352 --> 00:21:53,562
<font color="japanese">（ヨウタ）ぐわあっ！</c.japanese>

341
00:21:54,646 --> 00:21:55,647
<font color="japanese">ああ…</c.japanese>

342
00:21:57,816 --> 00:22:02,404
<font color="japanese">お前 どうなってんだ？　それ</c.japanese>

343
00:22:02,696 --> 00:22:04,156
<font color="japanese">（シューイチ）う うう…</c.japanese>

344
00:22:06,408 --> 00:22:11,413
{\an8}<font color="japanese">♪～</c.japanese>

345
00:23:27,364 --> 00:23:32,369
{\an8}<font color="japanese">～♪</c.japanese>

